UID:ccx_u696j5IR4UZLGNuYd
SUMMARY:EMBODIED ALTARS DANCE CLASS
DTSTAMP:20260401T021305Z
DTSTART:20260407T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:EMBODIED ALTARS is an all-levels dance class hosted by Daybreak
	 Star Radio. Designed by Indigenous Chicana artist and El Sueño director\,
	 Alicia Mullikin. Dancers will utilize Indigenous principles within moveme
	nt\, meditation\, and song as a way to practice gratitude\, honor the land
	\, and recognize their ancestors. The class is for those who are intereste
	d in reflection\, intention setting\, and a discovery of their own stories
	. No dance experience necessary. \n\nClass Time: Mondays\, 6:30-8PM \n\nNo
	 class 9/15/25\n\nNo class 10/13/25\n\nVenue: Daybreak Star Indian Cultura
	l Center\n\n5011 Bernie Whitebear Way\,\n\nSeattle\, WA 98199 \n\nSliding 
	Scale: $10-$20\\* per class. Sign Up Now! \n\n  \n\nThis venue is ADA acce
	ssible w/ ADA bathrooms and a wheelchair lift to the second floor. Class w
	ill be held in the ballroom space\, this area has 5 ADA parking spaces.\n\
	nThere are an additional 25 parking spots in our lot\, there is ample park
	ing space along the road leading up to Daybreak star as well as the Discov
	ery Park North Parking lot. \n\nWhat to bring: water\, comfortable clothes
	 to dance in\, journal\, your personal identity\, a desire to explore new 
	pathways and an open mind/heart. \n\nHosted at Daybreak Star Indian Cultur
	al Center\n\nProduced by United Indians of All Tribes Foundation\n\nIn Par
	tnership with El Sueno Dance & Daybreak Star Radio\n\n“Indigenize the Airw
	aves” “Art. Culture. Reclamation.” \n\n\\*Talk to us about BIPOC and Queer
	/LGBTQIA2S\\+ Scholorships\\* \n\nPlease contact @el.sueno.dance on IG for
	 private conversations about this topic.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/e
	vents/#/details/embodied-altars-dance-class/16539055/2026-04-06T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/embodied-altars-dance-cla
	ss/16539055/2026-04-06T00
LOCATION:Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center\, 5011 Bernie Whitebear Way\,
	 Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
